properties.title: BALTIC+ SEAL - Sea Level
properties.description: Providing a consistent description of the sea level variability in the Baltic Sea area in terms of seasonal and inter-annual variation and put the results in relationship with the forcing associated with this variability, using a developed dedicated coastal altimetry product
properties.osc:consortium: TECHNICAL UNIVERSITY OF MUNICH (DE),DANISH METEOROLOGICAL INSTITUTE (DK),FINNISH METEOROLOGICAL INSTITUTE (FI),TECHNICAL UNIVERSITY OF DENMARK (DK),UNIVERSITY COLLEGE CORK (IE)
